q1.question: Why does Vince Lombardi High School keep losing principals ?
q1.answer: ['The students keep driving them crazy, causing them to go to the mental hospital.', 'to nervous breakdowns']
q1.recall: Vince Lombardi High School keeps losing principals because the student body only cares about rock and roll music, causing the principals to suffer nervous breakdowns.
q1.vectordb: Vince Lombardi High School keeps losing principals because the students care about nothing but rock and roll music, causing the principals to suffer nervous breakdowns. Miss Togar, the new principal, vows to clean up the school and make it a center of learning. However, the students continue to prioritize their love for rock and roll, leading to conflicts with the principals. Ultimately, Miss Togar is taken away in an ambulance in a straight-jacket, becoming the latest principal to be carted away to a mental hospital.
